---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const pagePath = "/about";
const title = "About Pro Tiling | Sacramento Tile Contractor \u2014 10+ Years";
const description = "";
const canonical = "";
const ogTitle = "";
const ogDescription = "";
const ogType = "";
const ogUrl = "";
const schemaScripts = [];
const contentHtml = "<section class=\"page-hero\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"page-hero__content\">\n          <nav class=\"page-hero__breadcrumb\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\">\n            <a href=\"/\">Home</a><span>\u203a</span><span>About</span>\n          </nav>\n          <h1>Sacramento's Tile Contractor, Built on Craft</h1>\n          <p>Pro Tiling has been setting tile throughout the Sacramento area for over a decade. We're not the biggest contractor in town \u2014 and that's by design. We stay focused on tile, do it exceptionally well, and build relationships that bring clients back for every project.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"about-intro animate-on-scroll\">\n          <div class=\"about-img-wrap\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504307651254-35680f356dfd?w=700&q=80\" alt=\"Pro Tiling owner and tile contractor in Sacramento working on a custom installation\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"875\" />\n            <div class=\"why-grid__img-badge\" style=\"bottom:-16px;right:0;\">\n              <strong>10+</strong>\n              <span>Years<br>in Sacramento</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <span class=\"section-label\">Our Story</span>\n            <h2>Started in Sacramento. Stayed in Sacramento.</h2>\n            <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top:16px;\">Pro Tiling started as a straightforward idea: hire a tile contractor who actually takes pride in the work. That sounds basic \u2014 but anyone who's dealt with contractors who disappear mid-job, leave grout residue on the tile, or cut corners on waterproofing knows it's rarer than it should be.</p>\n            <p style=\"margin-top:16px;font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--mid-gray);line-height:1.8;\">Over the past 10+ years we've built a reputation across Sacramento, Elk Grove, Roseville, and Folsom for showing up on time, communicating clearly, and delivering work that genuinely exceeds what clients expected. Our business has grown almost entirely through referrals \u2014 which is the only growth metric that actually matters to us.</p>\n            <p style=\"margin-top:14px;font-size:0.9375rem;color:var(--mid-gray);line-height:1.8;\">We specialize in residential tile work because we believe depth of focus produces better results than breadth of services. Tile is all we do, so tile is what we do best.</p>\n            <div class=\"trust-badges\" style=\"justify-content:flex-start;margin-top:28px;\">\n              <div class=\"trust-badge\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/></svg>CA Licensed</div>\n              <div class=\"trust-badge\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"/></svg>Fully Insured</div>\n              <div class=\"trust-badge\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><polygon points=\"12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2\"/></svg>5-Star Rated</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section section--gray\" aria-labelledby=\"values-heading\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"text-center animate-on-scroll\">\n          <span class=\"section-label\">How We Work</span>\n          <h2 id=\"values-heading\">The Standards We Hold Ourselves To</h2>\n          <p style=\"max-width:480px;margin:12px auto 0;\">Every job we take on, no matter the size, gets our full attention. These are the principles that guide how we work.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about-values animate-on-scroll\">\n          <div class=\"value-card\">\n            <h4>Waterproofing First</h4>\n            <p>We never skip or shortchange the waterproofing step. It's not visible in the final result \u2014 but it's the difference between a shower that lasts 20 years and one that fails in 3.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"value-card\">\n            <h4>Honest Estimates</h4>\n            <p>We give you a detailed, written estimate before any work begins. If scope changes during the project, we tell you before we do the work \u2014 not after.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"value-card\">\n            <h4>Clean Job Sites</h4>\n            <p>We protect surrounding surfaces, contain the work area, and clean up every day before we leave. Your home doesn't become a construction site just because we're in it.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"value-card\">\n            <h4>Precision Over Speed</h4>\n            <p>We're not the fastest crew in Sacramento \u2014 we're the most careful. Layout planning, consistent joint spacing, and perfectly cut edges take time. That time shows in the finished product.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"value-card\">\n            <h4>Direct Communication</h4>\n            <p>When you call Pro Tiling, you talk to us. Not a dispatcher, not an answering service. We keep you informed throughout the project and respond quickly to questions.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"value-card\">\n            <h4>We Stand Behind Our Work</h4>\n            <p>If something isn't right after we leave, we come back and make it right. No runaround. That's a simple promise, and we keep it.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" aria-labelledby=\"areas-about-heading\">\n      <div class=\"container text-center animate-on-scroll\">\n        <span class=\"section-label\">Service Area</span>\n        <h2 id=\"areas-about-heading\">Proud to Serve Greater Sacramento</h2>\n        <p style=\"max-width:520px;margin:14px auto 28px;\">We work throughout the Sacramento metro and surrounding communities. If you're outside our typical range, call us \u2014 we'll let you know if we can make it work.</p>\n        <div class=\"areas-grid\" style=\"max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;\">\n          <div class=\"area-chip\" style=\"background:var(--off-white);border-color:var(--light-gray);color:var(--charcoal);\">Sacramento</div>\n          <div class=\"area-chip\" style=\"background:var(--off-white);border-color:var(--light-gray);color:var(--charcoal);\">Elk Grove</div>\n          <div class=\"area-chip\" style=\"background:var(--off-white);border-color:var(--light-gray);color:var(--charcoal);\">Roseville</div>\n          <div class=\"area-chip\" style=\"background:var(--off-white);border-color:var(--light-gray);color:var(--charcoal);\">Folsom</div>\n          <div class=\"area-chip\" style=\"background:var(--off-white);border-color:var(--light-gray);color:var(--charcoal);\">Natomas</div>\n          <div class=\"area-chip\" style=\"background:var(--off-white);border-color:var(--light-gray);color:var(--charcoal);\">Rancho Cordova</div>\n          <div class=\"area-chip\" style=\"background:var(--off-white);border-color:var(--light-gray);color:var(--charcoal);\">Citrus Heights</div>\n          <div class=\"area-chip\" style=\"background:var(--off-white);border-color:var(--light-gray);color:var(--charcoal);\">Rocklin</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-band\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"cta-band__inner\">\n          <h2>Let's work together on your <em>next tile project</em>.</h2>\n          <div class=\"cta-band__actions\">\n            <a href=\"tel:9165550100\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">(916) 555-0100</a>\n            <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn btn--outline\">Free Estimate</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>";
---

<BaseLayout
  pagePath={pagePath}
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonical={canonical}
  ogTitle={ogTitle}
  ogDescription={ogDescription}
  ogType={ogType}
  ogUrl={ogUrl}
  schemaScripts={schemaScripts}
>
  <Fragment set:html={contentHtml} />
</BaseLayout>